{"tid":1489103,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日澳門 明日香港","createTime":"2019-08-19T19:45:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T19:59:58.000Z","uid":271839,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d5d9e8aca60d83b0fded431d95a368b361c927c6","tid":1489103,"uid":271839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T19:45:49.000Z","msg":"相信大家今日都睇到澳門單新聞<br />\n一班澳門年輕人連和平默站既集會都俾人拉<br />\n同為特別行政區，依家連言論自由都無<br />\n我地香港人會甘心咩？<br />\n雖然我地818的確再次顯示出我地香港人既自律同團結，但係大家要記得<strong>我地仲係輸緊0:5啊！</strong> <br />\n五大訴求之中，政府一個都無回應啊！<br />\n甚至818 170萬人遊行，林奠都不屑我地，連記者會都無開去回應我地訴求啊！<br />\n大家唔可以鬆懈，我地要繼續任何行動，直到政府真真正正，正面咁回應啊！<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可！"},{"pid":"abe5b2439b06a51042bfc374d2314c679e7aa568","tid":1489103,"uid":271839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T19:46:58.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"0bf5b148d9f9f7d5c150568a265ab5ada513b219","tid":1489103,"uid":271839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T19:47:08.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"29d86fa153f8405a6a03240c2117bdfdfcafca1f","tid":1489103,"uid":271839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T19:47:18.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"06f7822384eafb3f8b57dbc862159a9b5abceaaf","tid":1489103,"uid":271839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T19:47:30.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"675d61f9fb542bca53625f2f892496fb54481c53","tid":1489103,"uid":12670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T19:51:05.000Z","msg":"幫你推 互推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有免費文宣啊<br />\n<br />\n［義憤民誠］地鐵報免費派十幾萬份文宣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1488994\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1488994</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7d315450a81bee3e43cd749d41b12d606ea38ef8","tid":1489103,"uid":226296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T19:59:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}